jade.util
Class Coord

java.lang.Object
  jade.util.Coord
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Coord>
public class Coord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Coord>, java.io.Serializable

Represents an integer cartesian coordinate. The Coord is not immutable, so care should be taken when assigning Coord reference to another when the copy constructor should have been used.
